---
interface Props {
  className?: string;
}

const { className = '' } = Astro.props;

const INSTRUCTOR_NAME = 'Israel Castro';
const INSTRUCTOR_IMAGE = '/images/photo.png';
---

<section
  class={`py-20 lg:py-32 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 font-display ${className}`}
>
  <!-- Main Card Container -->
  <div
    class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-5xl flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-white shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/50 border border-slate-100 lg:flex-row animate-on-scroll"
    data-animation="scale-in"
  >
    <!-- Left Column: Visual & Quick Actions -->
    <div
      class="relative flex w-full flex-col items-center justify-center bg-slate-50/50 p-8 lg:w-1/3 lg:border-r lg:border-slate-100"
    >
      <!-- Decorative background element -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(#3713ec_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:16px_16px] opacity-[0.03]"
      >
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
        <!-- Profile Image with Primary Accent Ring -->
        <div class="group relative">
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-purple-600 opacity-20 blur transition duration-500 group-hover:opacity-40"
          >
          </div>
          <div
            class="h-48 w-48 rounded-full bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat shadow-2xl ring-4 ring-white relative z-10"
            style={`background-image: url("${INSTRUCTOR_IMAGE}");`}
          >
          </div>
          <!-- Verified Badge -->
          <div
            class="absolute bottom-2 right-2 z-20 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-primary shadow-xl ring-4 ring-slate-50"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px] fill-[1]"
              >verified</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Social Actions -->
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a
            class="group flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white text-slate-400 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all shadow-sm border border-slate-100"
            href="#"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[22px]">link</span>
          </a>
          <a
            class="group flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white text-slate-400 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all shadow-sm border border-slate-100"
            href="#"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[22px]"
              >alternate_email</span
            >
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column: Biography & Credentials -->
    <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col p-8 lg:p-12">
      <!-- Header Section -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <span
          class="mb-3 inline-block rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-4 py-1 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-primary border border-primary/10"
        >
          Sobre el Instructor
        </span>
        <h2
          class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-text-main sm:text-4xl leading-tight"
        >
          {INSTRUCTOR_NAME}
        </h2>
        <p
          class="mt-2 text-lg font-black text-primary sm:text-xl italic opacity-90"
        >
          Contador Público y Programador
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio Body -->
      <div
        class="mb-10 max-w-none text-text-muted text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium"
      >
        <p class="mb-4">
          Israel es un experto pionero en la intersección de la contabilidad y
          la tecnología. Como fundador de <strong class="text-text-main"
            >TodoConta</strong
          >, ha dedicado su carrera a automatizar procesos contables complejos
          mediante el uso de Inteligencia Artificial.
        </p>
        <p>
          Su doble formación le permite entender los dolores de cabeza fiscales
          y traducirlos en soluciones de código eficientes. Su misión es clara:
          ayudar a los contadores a perder el miedo a la tecnología y
          convertirla en su mejor aliada.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Credentials / Description List -->
      <div
        class="grid gap-x-8 gap-y-6 border-t border-slate-100 pt-10 sm:grid-cols-2"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px]"
              >history_edu</span
            >
            <p
              class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest opacity-70 leading-none"
            >
              Experiencia
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base font-extrabold text-text-main">
            12+ años en contabilidad mexicana (SAT, RESICO, CFDI)
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px]">psychology</span
            >
            <p
              class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest opacity-70 leading-none"
            >
              Especialidad
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base font-extrabold text-text-main">
            Flujos híbridos de IA para contadores
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="col-span-full mt-4 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-6 border border-slate-100/50"
        >
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div
              class="mt-1 flex h-10 w-10 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary text-white shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 rotate-3"
            >
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]"
                >rocket_launch</span
              >
            </div>
            <div>
              <p
                class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 mb-1 leading-none"
              >
                Filosofía
              </p>
              <p class="text-base font-extrabold text-text-main m-0">
                Empoderar a la próxima generación de contadores digitales.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
